---
title: Bacon, Mushroom & Parmesan Risotto with Parsley & Garden Salad
description: Risotto is so delicious, but the prospect of all that stirring can sometimes be a bit daunting! Our version lets you put your
risotto in the oven and forget about it until it's time to eat. All the creamy, luxurious texture with none of the elbow work!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651d78aaa19829649acd92af-19cc3d06.jpeg
